{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"21":"Funerals (Kitab Al-Jana'iz)"},"section_detail":{"21":{"hadithnumber_first":3089,"hadithnumber_last":3241,"arabicnumber_first":3089,"arabicnumber_last":3241}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3121,"arabicnumber":3121,"text":"Rapporté par Ma'qil ibn Yasar رضي الله عنه : Le Prophète ﷺ a dit : « Récitez la sourate Ya-Sin sur vos mourants. » Ceci est la version d’Ibn al-Ala","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":21,"hadith":33}}]}